For those that were interested, I posted a picture of the adjuster here:

http://www.type2.com/des/vw/bluto/dash

Scroll down to the lower picture if necessary.  Thanks to Greg Thompson for reminding me that the adjuster is not a small screw, but rather a "nub" which must be grabbed with a small pair of pliers.  The nub is sort of the reverse of a standard slotted machine screw would be, if that makes sense.



